OL,3,CThousands sign petition calling for
OL,4,Caction at road fatality hotspot
OL,6,FThousands of people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition calling for action to be
OL,8,Ftaken to prevent further tragedy on a
OL,9,Fbusy A-road near RNAS Culdrose.
OL,11,FFour people have been killed in
OL,12,Fincidents on a stretch of the A3083
OL,13,Fnear the naval airbase since 2018.
OL,15,FMost recently Samuel Vass, a 22 year
OL,16,Fold engineer, died following a
OL,17,Fcollision with another car.
OL,19,FDaniel Thirkill, who started the
OL,20,Fpetition, is calling for average speed
OL,21,Fcameras to be installed on the road.
