OL,6,FMr Thirkill said "We can't afford to
OL,7,Fignore this any longer. Recent
OL,8,Fincidents have highlighted the urgent
OL,9,Fneed for action, and every day that
OL,10,Fpasses without change puts more lives
OL,11,Fat risk.
OL,13,F"By implementing a 60mph average speed
OL,14,Fcamera, we can drastically reduce the
OL,15,Flikelihood of high-speed collisions
OL,16,Fand save lives."
OL,18,FIn December 2022, two aircraft
OL,19,Fengineers based at the nearby RNAS
OL,20,FCuldrose died when the car they were
OL,21,Ftravelling in crashed into another car.
