OL,6,FIn 2018, 18 year old Lottie Rees was
OL,7,Fkilled in a motorcycle crash.
OL,9,F"We can't afford to ignore this any
OL,10,Flonger," added Mr Thirkill.
OL,12,F"Recent incidents have highlighted the
OL,13,Furgent need for action, and every day
OL,14,Fthat passes without change puts more
OL,15,Flives at risk."
OL,17,FIn response to the petition, Cornwall
OL,18,FCouncil said "We are committed to
OL,19,Freducing the number of people killed
OL,20,Fand seriously injured on our roads
OL,21,Fthrough our ongoing work with partners.
